Package tools

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheckSum
    CheckSum class is responsible for giving checksum results according to the selected encryption algorithm.
    DataBase
    DataBase class is responsible for managing all the serialized information related to the UnDupeKeeper for later use.
    FileQueue
    FileQueue class is an structure just for helping associate a file path to some action.
    FileTableModel
    FileTableModel class provides a render set of tools to display files in a table.
    FileTreeCellRenderer
    FileTreeCellRenderer class provides a render set of tools to display files in a tree.
    Logger
    Logger class is responsible for centralize debug and message mechanism, allowing developer to use filters and levels of displaying message, controlling source code by sectors.
    ReportGenerator
    ReportGenerator class is responsible for providing complete tree information regarding to directories and its file contents.
    SettingsHandler
    SettingsHandler class is the main object to store all settings from UnDupeKeeper for save and restore settings data in just only one place.
    TrayImage
    TrayImage class is responsible for creating and set the System Tray Icon image.
    Utils
    Utils class is responsible for providing a set of miscellaneous tools
